15 (f) Is the aggressor violently or constantly jealous or does the
16 aggressor control most of your daily activities?
17 (g) Did you leave or separate from the aggressor after
18 cohabitating with the aggressor or being married to the aggressor?
19 (h) Is the aggressor unemployed?
